About Beech Hill
 



Beech Hill traces its origin back to 1932 when a former partner’s family established a retail brokerage firm.
In 1970, Paul Cantor joined that firm and has since served as managing partner and/or president of the firm and its successor organizations. Paul and Joseph Weiss, our other founding principal partner, have continuously worked together under varied market conditions. They are committed to the firm’s proven investment process.


Today, the firm operates as two companies, Beech Hill Securities, Inc. and Beech Hill Advisors, Inc.
Our success through the years across both organizations goes beyond our investment results. Our clients are confident that they are being well advised and given wise counsel.



