Strategic Alliances
Beech Hill Securities



African Alliance is an investment banking group operating in Africa. They provide local and on-the-ground investment banking services across the African continent.
Key & Company LLC provides strategic and financial advisory services to clients in the food and agriculture industries.
Penbrook Management LLC is an independent SEC registered investment advisor to individuals and institutions seeking a personalized approach to meet their financial goals. Our managers specialize in “bottoms up” stock picking, investing in companies that we regard as undervalued and often misunderstood by investors.


RM Global Partners is an investment banking firm specialized in life sciences. We provide independent advice on transactions and strategy to clients globally, addressing their strategic, M&A, investment and financing needs.
Santangel’s Review is dedicated to finding and analyzing undiscovered investors. It is the creator and organizer of the Santangel’s Investor Forum, and invitation-only salon that brings together investors and allocators from around the globe to discuss specific stock picks and investment themes.



