Core Strategy
Will Wurm




 Q2 2017 : Improving Economic Backdrop
Summary: The second quarter of 2017 provided modest positive returns in the domestic equity markets with the S&P 500 up approximately 2.5% for the quarter bringing the year to date gain to 9%. The U.S. economy continues on its muted path with ongoing gains in consumer spending and business fixed investment paired with elevated business optimism.
